cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.ET, cs.SE

Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with estimating the unobserved amount of PV generation and demand in a power distribution network, which involves modeling and control of the system.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes four estimation algorithms for disaggregating PV production, which involve machine learning and statistical techniques.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes machine learning-based algorithms for estimating PV generation and demand.
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): The paper deals with emerging technologies such as PV installations and battery systems for PV self-consumption.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software engineering aspects such as implementation and testing of the proposed algorithms.
